    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>BRICS CCI WE – Women Empowerment Vertical proudly launches the 3rd edition of its flagship Global Women Leadership Programme (GWLP)!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>This transformative initiative empowers women professionals and entrepreneurs across BRICS+ nations and partner countries through a thoughtfully curated mentorship and learning journey.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>With Nippon Paint GroupAR as the Lead Programme Partner, and ThinkStartup along with Sheatwork as Knowledge Partners, GWLP continues its mission of building future-ready women leaders by offering:<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>- Real-world skills<br>- Global exposure<br>- Mentorship from experts<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Programme Highlights:<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The top three participants globally will win a fully funded trip to India to attend the Convocation Ceremony—an enriching opportunity to network, exchange ideas, and expand horizons.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The best project leveraging Nudge Theory will be honoured with a trophy at the BRICS CCI WE Annual Summit &amp; Felicitations 2026, in collaboration with the Cheistha Kochhar Foundation.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Applications are now open!<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Apply by 20th September 2025 <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Link to apply: https:\/\/shorturl.at\/YTkUJ<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>#GlobalWomenLeadership #WomenEmpowerment #WomenEntrepreneurs #GWLP2025 #BRICS #Sheatwork<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
