    "post_content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>  Score.org DATE &amp; TIME: June 16, 2020, 11:00am EDT<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>In this webinar, you can get insights from four exceptional women entrepreneurs - Laurel Delaney, Betsy Mikesell, Angie White and Dr. Sonat Birnecker Hart. It will cover how to innovate and disrupt the world of business – to grow faster, stronger, and expand globally for a better future.<\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It will provide information on why women rule in the global marketplace and why a kickstarter campaign is important to consider. And when you start off and get to the brand communication, why a good design makes a strong first impression and how patents can safeguard your invention. Other learnings will include - how to pivot a business in a crisis, how to follow your passion and turn a family business into a global powerhouse, how setting up an ecommerce platform can take a business global. It could also assist you to assess who might be your next best partner in business!  <\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Know more: <a href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2YjYahN\">https:\/\/bit.ly\/2YjYahN<\/a><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
