    "post_date": "2019-12-26 11:12:48",
    "post_date_gmt": "2019-12-26 05:42:48",
    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> When: 12<sup>th<\/sup>&nbsp;January 2020  <\/p><p> Where: THE LALIT, Chandigarh <\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>America's most successful entrepreneur summit launches its second Indian edition in Chandigarh -&nbsp; to share their unfiltered, unconventional and unexpected insights into what it takes to launch, sustain and grow a business.<\/p>\n<p>Organized by Entrepreneur media, Entrepreneur L!ve is America’s top entrepreneur summit bringing together a powerful lineup of speakers, such as&nbsp;<strong>Maria Sharapova (Professional Tennis Player &amp; Entrepreneur) and Danica Patrick (GoDaddy Entrepreneur &amp; Former Race Car Driver). <\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Launching its second Indian edition in Chandigarh, Entrepreneur Live&nbsp;will bring together over 250 entrepreneurs and investors. There is a chance &nbsp;to establish new ties, form new avenues, create new investment opportunities, address complexities that affect the ecosystem and highlight the importance of entrepreneurship. &nbsp;The mission of this meet is to support entrepreneurs by offering learning, mentorship, networking and funding opportunities. The day summit will showcase upcoming startups, an experiential zone with top of the line suppliers, startup kick off, workshops and summit for Entrepreneurs, SMEs and Startups.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/39b7xEZ\">Book Your Seat<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->",
