    "post_date_gmt": "2019-12-26 05:40:30",
    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> When: Dec 28, Sat 9am to 6pm <\/p><p> Where: Indraprastha Institute of Information Technology Delhi, Okhla Industrial Estate, Phase III, Near Govind Puri Metro Station, New Delhi <\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>The workshop is being conducted by APROS (Academy for Professional Skills) and the theme for the workshop is -<strong>\"DECODING ENTREPRENEURSHIP\".<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>The event will present several eminent speakers, who will try to decode \"the formula\" for entrepreneurship - by sharing their life experiences. This will take you into a journey, if you have any idea of starting off as an entrepreneur, and will set you thinking, as you comprehend the essence of being an entrepreneur. The speakers include - <strong>Vamsi Krishna <\/strong>(Director of Startup Grind X, CEO of Saffro Studios, <strong>Sam Baisla<\/strong> Founder CEO of Nexel, Brand Samosa and Startup India Foundation, <strong>Nitin Sethi <\/strong>(Vice President of Indigo Airlines), <strong>Musee Pugazhendi <\/strong>(Co-Founder and CEO of Skill Bench).<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2QjHMtx\">Know More<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->",
