    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p>When: December 29, Sun, 11 am – 1 pm<\/p><p>Where: Chaayos, M 66, Plot No 3, Connaught Circus, Road, Block M, Connaught Place, New Delhi<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>Startkom is a startup community that organizes startup events in Delhi every weekend. So, if you are an Entrepreneur, Business Person, Startup Consultant, Corporate Professional, Mentor, Investor or Student,  then these events can be truly interesting experiences. Plus they can also inspire you to start off your own business.<\/p>\n<p>You get the opportunity here to connect with the right people on a single platform. It sets you off on the right track – networking. It goes without saying, how important networking is for any one who aspires to start off your own business or launch your own products.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2QjkF27\">Know More<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->",
