    "post_date_gmt": "2019-12-17 07:44:45",
    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> When: January 28 - January 29, 2020 <\/p><p> Where: Nariman Point, Mumbai &nbsp; <\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>The focus will be on - The Decade of Start-ups. The 11<sup>th<\/sup>edition of TiEcon Mumbai has a vibrant theme&nbsp;<strong>“Decade of the Startups. Future is Now”. <\/strong>The 2-day program is designed to contemplate on the future of ideas, entrepreneurship and the leadership needed to embrace, navigate through successful break-throughs &amp; journeys untrodden &nbsp;so far.<\/p>\n<p><strong>Past eminent speakers at TiEcon Mumbai 2019 have been - <\/strong>&nbsp;N. Chandrasekaran - Chairman, Tata Sons, Narayana Murthy – Chairman, &nbsp;Emeritus, Infosys; Mohandas Pai – Founder &amp; Chairman, Manipal Global Education; Anupam Mittal - Founder &amp; CEO, Shaadi.com; Rakesh Jhunjhunwala - CEO, Rare Enterprises; Binny Bansal, Co-founder, Flipkart.com, Ronnie Screwvala - Co-founder, Upgrad amongst others.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2PqOgHR\">Book Tickets<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
