    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> When: December 19, 2019  <\/p><p> Where: Mumbai <\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>The event is organized by TIE-Mumbai. Here, Duff &amp; Phelps invites you to a session on <strong>Fundraising Essentials for Startups <\/strong>where industry experts will discuss a variety of topics - valuation, due diligence, legal and fund raising issues involved in the investment process of startups. It is a great opportunity for entrepreneurs, investors and venture capitalists (VCs) to network and gain in-depth knowledge on startup funding.<\/p>\n<p>Topics that will be covered include: Understanding key legal issues and decoding term sheets, Checks and balances as startups seek venture funding,  How to prepare for the financial due diligence process,  Valuation of tech startups, How VCs make investment choices.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2PW6T5D\">Know More<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
