    "post_content": "<!-- wp:quote -->\n<blockquote class=\"wp-block-quote\"><p> When: December 18, 2019 <\/p><p>Where: B.K.C Mumbai<\/p><\/blockquote>\n<!-- \/wp:quote -->\n\n<p>Come face-to-face with Sasha Mirchandani – Founder and Managing Director, KAE Capitals and Co-founder Mumbai Angels. Previously, he was at Blue Run Ventures as Managing Director for the India operations.  Prior to that, he was CEO and Founder of Imercius Technologies. Earlier he was at Mirc Electronics (Onida) where he was Head of Corporate Affairs and new business. His varied investments include - Inmobi, Healthkart,1Mg, Myntra, Porter and Fractal Analytics. He sits on the Boards of Hathway Cable and Datacom Limited, Nazara Technologies Limited, Ador Welding, Healthkart, Young Presidents' Organization (Mumbai Chapter) and Mumbai Angels Venture Mentors among others; previously he was on the Boards of Fractal Analytics and Myntra.<\/p>\n\n<!-- wp:button -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\" href=\"https:\/\/bit.ly\/2S62NKy\">Know More<\/a><\/div>\n<!-- \/wp:button -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><\/p>\n<!-- \/wp:paragraph -->",
